       . Game Information

       Release Date...: 10/07/2008           Discs........: 1
       Game Type......: Action               Protection...: None
       Image Type.....: ISO                  Archive Type.: .rar


       . Game Summary

       "Rhiannon: Curse of the Four Branches", based on the classic
       Welsh "Four Branches" legends, is set in a mystical place on
       the Celtic fringes of Britain, a place where myth and magic spill
       into reality, threatening the sanity of a teenage girl and bringing an
       ancient battle for revenge to a remote Welsh farmstead.


       . Installation Notes

       1. Unpack
       2. Mount
       3. Install
       4. Play!                                                                                                                                

                                                                               
